  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个内存检测流程图，核心逻辑是根据可用RAM大小来决定返回的块大小。起点是\"Start: Check Available RAM\"，然后做一个判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start: Check Available RAM",
        "Available RAM (GB)?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，起点是绿色风格的开始节点。判断节点用菱形对吧？那判断之后有多少个分支？我需要确认一下具体的内存区间划分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start: Check Available RAM",
        "Available RAM (GB)?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分支比较多。小于1GB返回64KB，1到2GB返回128KB，2到3GB返回256KB，3到4GB和4到6GB都是512KB，6到8GB和8到12GB都是1MB，12到16GB和16到24GB都是1.5MB，24到32GB和等于32GB都是3MB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 64 KB",
        "Return 128 KB",
        "Return 256 KB",
        "Return 512 KB",
        "Return 1 MB",
        "Return 1.5 MB",
        "Return 3 MB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "我整理一下：3-4GB和4-6GB合并到512KB，6-8GB和8-12GB合并到1MB，12-16GB和16-24GB合并到1.5MB，24-32GB和等于32GB合并到3MB。这样设计是为了减少返回类型的数量对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 512 KB",
        "Return 1 MB",
        "Return 1.5 MB",
        "Return 3 MB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这样。另外还需要一个错误处理分支，如果检测过程出错，要fallback到512KB。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error: Fallback to 512 KB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我把错误节点用红色标注。所有分支最后都汇聚到一个统一的\"Return\"节点吗？这样结构更清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error: Fallback to 512 KB",
        "Return"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，所有路径最终都汇聚到Return节点。开始节点和Return节点都用绿色，判断节点用蓝色，错误节点用红色，这样视觉区分明显。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start: Check Available RAM",
        "Available RAM (GB)?",
        "Error: Fallback to 512 KB",
        "Return"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先搭建主干结构：Start节点指向判断节点，判断节点引出各个内存区间的分支。每个返回节点都连到最终的Return。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start: Check Available RAM",
        "Available RAM (GB)?",
        "Return"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我需要确认一下字节数的标注。64KB要写成65,536 bytes，128KB是131,072 bytes，这样开发人员能直接看到精确数值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 64 KB",
        "Return 128 KB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，我会在每个返回节点里加上具体的字节数。256KB是262,144 bytes，512KB是524,288 bytes，1MB是1,048,576 bytes，1.5MB是1,572,864 bytes，3MB是3,145,728 bytes。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Return 256 KB",
        "Return 512 KB",
        "Return 1 MB",
        "Return 1.5 MB",
        "Return 3 MB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有错误fallback节点也要标注字节数，同样是512KB对应524,288 bytes，这样和正常的512KB分支保持一致。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error: Fallback to 512 KB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我已经把主干连好了。现在处理判断节点的标签：小于1GB、1-2GB、2-3GB这些区间标注都加上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Available RAM (GB)?"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "注意一下，24-32GB和等于32GB是两个独立的条件判断，虽然都返回3MB，但标签要分开写，一个是\"24 - 32 GB\"，一个是\"= 32 GB\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
